00:56:11.329 --> 00:56:14.010
It's not exactly what you
expect to meet at random.

00:56:14.010 --> 00:56:16.876
And then to give you a third
example, there was a house

00:56:16.876 --> 00:56:18.894
called--it's wrong now,
Kirkland House,

00:56:18.894 --> 00:56:20.909
is that right?
Kirkland House.

00:56:20.909 --> 00:56:24.460
And Kirkland House was known to
be the jock house,

00:56:24.460 --> 00:56:27.502
the athlete house,
and of course this being

00:56:27.502 --> 00:56:31.559
Harvard that meant that everyone
